仔😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼高帥肯用年輕人。佢話就排在奧歷治同史獨。但睇得高師鐘意佢多d.<br />\n<br />\n前2場友誼賽都出佢多d<br />\n<br />\n如果干地肯俾機會佢的就唔會走了。<br />\n<br />\n排到第4前鋒。點算呀師父"},{"pid":"c6fab1d75d9affbbe03db56a50242754079c1e52","tid":335411,"uid":45917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實唔明蘇蘭基點解走<br />\n用黎打下後備 間中正選都好<br />\n<br />\n利果邊競爭 點睇都唔會細唔過車仔😂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼高帥肯用年輕人。佢話就排在奧歷治同史獨。但睇得高師鐘意佢多d.<br />\n<br />\n前2場友誼賽都出佢多d<br />\n<br />\n如果干地肯俾機會佢的就唔會走了。<br />\n<br />\n排到第4前鋒。點算呀師父</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以干地根本食古不化 用人唯親"},{"pid":"da5f3020efca5741a494ccb4e7c31475dab0849b","tid":335411,"uid":45917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"miss you....costq"},{"pid":"5154d10dfb390aefd7b490190efdfcddb6eb60f8","tid":335411,"uid":50608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:45:37.000Z","msg":"巴舒坐足一季 干地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dabe991a4fc0f58acfe1ca8420054caa4135f2","tid":335411,"uid":45917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:48:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>miss you....costq</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">costa</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ee5b19148c46fe4e153f07698c79d63ccd8e6a3a","tid":335411,"uid":72415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}